data.meta_description:
19K likes, 157 comments - rapunzelexplores on October 31, 2023: ": For decades, Steve Jobs’ house (former CEO of Apple), situated across the street from Google co-founder Larry Page’s residence, has been hosting a Halloween block party every year on October 31st! This year’s highlight was spooky Barbie and Ken’s house. The entire Santa Rita and Waverly Street in Palo Alto transforms into the perfect Halloween destination for you and your kids. Imagine a street where billionaires reside, generously offering full-sized bars, toys, engaging board games, and, of course, an abundance of candies as treats.

There are also many DJ performances and photo booths hosted by various other families. 

⏱️ 6pm-9pm, 31st October every year.

Make sure to save this incredible Silicon Valley block party for your next Halloween celebration!

#halloween #halloween2023 #paloalto #siliconvalley #stevejobs #california #sanfrancisco #sfbayarea #bayarea #travel #explore #blockparty".
